<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="22Jun1930"><font color="red">22 June 1930</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver from Lucia Joyce): My father&apos;s sight gets better slowly every day. He says the enclosed explains the mystery of J.J. &hellip; He would like you to send him a guide to Wales as one cannot find one here in the time </div>
